# Constants Guide

The [`src/constants/`](mdc:src/constants) directory contains application-wide constants, enums, and configuration values.

- [`constants.ts`](mdc:src/constants/constants.ts): Defines color arrays, data types, default values, and debug flags.
- [`enums.ts`](mdc:src/constants/enums.ts): Enumerations for use throughout the app.
- [`ThemeSetting.ts`](mdc:src/constants/ThemeSetting.ts): Theme-related constants.
- [`HttpStatusCode.ts`](mdc:src/constants/HttpStatusCode.ts): HTTP status code mappings.

Constants are imported wherever fixed values or configuration are needed, ensuring consistency and maintainability.
